room_title: Escape room "Honeymoon Suite" by Escape Chambers in Des Moines
room_description: Two of your best friends are going on their honeymoon in Vegas but after a week of hearing nothing from them, it's time to call the cops. While they assure you there was "no foul play" and they must have skipped town, you know something else is going on. It's up to you to find out what happened but you could never imagine what darkness lurks in Sin City...
